snippet.title: CP3D - Card Jitsu Fire
snippet.description:
CP3D Ninjas can continue their journey at the Fire Dojo. Challenge fellow ninjas, in the Card-Jitsu Fire game. Defeat Sensei to earn your Fire Suit and become a powerful Fire Ninja.  

All penguins can earn their Black Belts at the Dojo by playing the Card-Jitsu game. Have you taken the ninja journey?


Waddle on!


Website: https://cp3d.org/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/CP3DOfficial
Discord: https://discord.gg/mEV33ZtcxM
